      <span class="nav-card-title">Daily &amp; Weekly Reviews</span>
      <span class="nav-card-desc">STB exports &mdash; session summaries</span>
    </a>
    <a class="nav-card" href="https://github.com/drasticstatic/trading-assistant-public-preview/blob/main/smarttrader-ai/reviews/pattern_tracker.md" target="_blank">
