    </a>
    <a class="nav-card" href="https://github.com/drasticstatic/trading-assistant-public-preview/tree/main/data/inevitrade%20progression" target="_blank">
      <span class="nav-card-icon">&#127891;</span>
      <span class="nav-card-title">Inevitrade Progression</span>
      <span class="nav-card-desc">IT Foundation coaching progress + notes</span>
